name: Potato
body: Potatoes are great because you can eat them. You can mash them, fry them, or put them in a stew. Mashed potatoes are tasty with steak. Fried potatoes go good with cheeseburgers and sandwiches. When yo put potatoes in a stew you make that stew at least 10 times better. Potatoes are the best type of food because they are filling and taste good. ![](http://www.google.com/imgres?imgurl=http://vignette2.wikia.nocookie.net/uncyclopedia/images/4/4a/Holy-potato.jpg/revision/latest%253Fcb%253D20090618200658&imgrefurl=http://uncyclopedia.wikia.com/wiki/File:Holy-potato.jpg&h=320&w=320&tbnid=3U_XLU44c3M2KM:&docid=uaUBldINXF83YM&ei=HL_YVaWhGoKSoQStzpOgBQ&tbm=isch&ved=0CB0QMygAMABqFQoTCKWf_tCovccCFQJJiAodLecEVA)
